item.title: Webclient GAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAH
item.dc:creator: @JavaTC JavaTC
item.description:
@JavaTC wrote:

Your problem is your client is loading the cache, that’s why it’s so big. Tell it to download & extract the cache to the C:/, remove the cache from the client, and re-jar it.
